snippet.title: Demon Tides - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Demon Tides on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2585890/Demon_Tides/

Follow Beebz and her crew on a journey of self-discovery as they travel the vast oceans of Ragnar's Rock.

Navigate the open seas and explore each distant structure, uncovering every
hidden nook and cranny with your diverse, expressive move-set. Beat challenges or find hidden chests to collect talismans along the way that modify and even expand your abilities or switch up your drip with a plethora of discoverable outfits!

And never forget, you're not alone in this journey! Compete with other players for speedrunning times by challenging their ghosts or tag a wall and share your message in the form of graffiti with the entire world!
